text: Apona yunnanensis is a moth in the family Eupterotidae. It was described by Rudolf Mell in 1929. It is found in China. ==Subspecies== *Apona yunnanensis yunnanensis *Apona yunnanensis alticola Mell, 1937 (China: Yunnan) ==References== Category:Moths described in 1929 Category:Eupterotinae
title: Apona yunnanensis
